data.description: Discover the allure of this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home on Flatwoods Road. Modern finishes grace every corner, complemented by a bonus room for added versatility. The basement unveils a workshop and expansive storage options. Step onto the inviting back deck, complete with a fire pit and above-ground pool, creating a perfect outdoor retreat. Situated on a generous 1.45-acre lot, this residence seamlessly blends style and functionality. With a plethora of appealing features, including ample outdoor space, this home invites you to experience a lifestyle of comfort and sophistication. Don't miss out—schedule your showing today and envision the possibilities!
